nodes.text: Ch. Empress Sunwinds Messenger Chung-Chung LaFlorin III. Dotty
Ch. Empress Sunwinds Messenger Chung-Chung LaFlorin III. Dotty, or Dotty for short, was a pet voorpak belonging to the female Lady Deprovan.
Dotty was first mentioned in a mission terminal quest in the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided.
